timeline.bodyText:
This reads strangely to me.
I realise that, in terms of readability, it's logically equivalent to the isAllowedByLicenseAndSecurity method, but here with no parameters, it just looks like a mistake.
Given this is the only place it's called, I would just replace it with isAllowedByLicenseAndSecurity(OperationMode.BASIC, true, false, true);

